# Gitleaks ignore file for Bit2Me MCP Server
# This file excludes paths from secret scanning.
#
# Policy:
#  - Never exclude source/test/doc directories. Real secrets accidentally
#    committed there MUST be detected. False positives in those areas
#    must be handled with explicit regex entries in the [allowlist] block
#    of `.gitleaks.toml`, not by excluding entire trees.
#  - Only build artefacts and lock files (which contain dependency
#    checksums that look like high-entropy blobs) are excluded here.

# Build artifacts
build/
coverage/
dist/
node_modules/

# Lock files (may contain dependency checksums that look like secrets)
package-lock.json
pnpm-lock.yaml
